    <h2>Always Looking for the Best Deal for You</h2>
    <p>
      We don't push one VPP platform or one electricity retailer. We started with Amber Energy because we thought they were the best option at the time. Now we also use Glowbird, Tango, and others depending on what makes the most sense for each client.
    </p>
    <p>
      Recently we discovered that Glowbird offers a plan where you can force charge your battery from the grid for free between 11am and 2pm. For some of our clients, especially during those three or four winter months when solar production isn't enough to fully charge the battery, this is a better strategy than Amber's wholesale pricing model.
    </p>
    <p>
      The right plan depends on your system size, your phases, your usage patterns, and the time of year. We model all of this using your actual interval data and recommend the plan that gives you the best result. If a better plan comes along next year, we'll let you know.
    </p>
